Package: checklist
Title: Structure and Reproducibility Checks for Student Assignments
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Colin",
           family = "Rundel",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rundel@gmail.com")
Description: Tools for instructors to automatically check the structure
    and reproducibility of student assignment submissions. Includes
    checks that required files are present and disallowed files are
    absent, that all package dependencies are available, and that
    'R Markdown' and 'Quarto' documents render successfully. Checks can
    be run locally or with continuous integration services such as
    'GitHub Actions' to provide students with immediate feedback on
    their submissions.
